      <label class="med-gray h5 mb2 block">Instructor</label>
      <div class="flex underline-link mb3">
        <div class="flex-none mr3">
            <img width="80" src="https://hackdesign.imgix.net/curators/josephhuang@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails-2.1.4&dpr=2&w=80&h=80&fit=crop&fm=jpeg&auto=format&mask=ellipse&s=252ef4141fadde36e977f8dde19bd695" alt="Josephhuang@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails 2.1" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Joseph Huang</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Founding Designer, 
              <a target="_blank" href="http://swell.am">Swell</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm the Founding Designer of <a href="http://www.swell.am" target="_blank">Swell</a>, a delightful way to discover podcasts.  Previously I designed Kingdoms of <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kingdoms-camelot-battle-for/id476546099?mt=8" target="_blank">Camelot</a>, the #1 Top Grossing App of 2012 on the Apple App Store and worked at BlackBerry and Qualcomm.  I like making things, technology and the great outdoors.</p>
        </div>
      </div>


